<L>__{interior dining hall night}
<A>__{the orphans are watching king kong, the part when the giant ape first captures the screaming fay wray. intercut kong with the orphans' rapt faces. homer sits near the front, mesmerized by the film. dr. larch and angela sit by the projector; larch is reading a letter. fuzzy points to the screen.}
<C>__{fuzzy}
<P>__{(coughing)}
<D>__{he thinks she's his mother!}
