<D>__{they just want you to hire some new help.}
<C>__{larch}
<D>__{some new things would be useful. i don't need any "new help."}
<A>__{the film breaks to huge cries of disappointment from the orphans. fuzzy coughs and coughs while larch fumbles with the projector. angela turns on the light while larch squints at the broken film. the orphans are chanting, "kong! kong!"}
<C>__{larch}
<D>__{homer! i need you!}
